# Day03

## 2nd Part

Given the following binaries in the diagnostics report:

```
00100
11110
10110
10111
10101
01111
00111
11100
10000
11001
00010
01010
```

partitioning the binaries into two lists a left most bit position results in:

For ones (oxygen generator):

```
00100 11110 10110 10111 10101 01111 00111 11100 10000 11001 00010 01010 
11110 10110 10111 10101 11100 10000 11001
10110 10111 10101 10000
10110 10111 10101
10110 10111
10111
```

For zeros (co2 scrubber)

```
00100 11110 10110 10111 10101 01111 00111 11100 10000 11001 00010 01010 
00100 01111 00111 00010 01010
01111 01010
01010
```
